    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your asteroid is a frontier. It's massive, procedurally unique to you, and holds hours of exploration. What you uncover is yours alone. Exovia is a relaxing space mining, engineering, automation, and logistics sim.  Every mined resource becomes a floater, a resource for you to build everything you need for constructing humanity's warp gate.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mining creates chaos. Floaters scatter in every direction, bouncing off walls and each other. Design systems that catch, accelerate, sort, and process them into organized streams that flow exactly where you engineered them to go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/47e865c5ae2ffe08a3165009ac3bc287.poster.avif?t=1772015010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/47e865c5ae2ffe08a3165009ac3bc287.webm?t=1772015010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/47e865c5ae2ffe08a3165009ac3bc287.mp4?t=1772015010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/3540e39c7fdba011ec0eb357b7b0913e.avif?t=1772015010\" width=616 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No conveyor belts, teleportation, or magic inventory. Just you, Newtonian physics, and an asteroid full of drifting materials.<br><br>Build sorting junctions, accelerator networks, and production chains that grow from simple fixes into sprawling supply systems. Higher output demands smarter logistics and every solution opens a new problem worth solving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/fee971ae18374216b8f853839b7f16f7.poster.avif?t=1772015010\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/fee971ae18374216b8f853839b7f16f7.webm?t=1772015010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/fee971ae18374216b8f853839b7f16f7.mp4?t=1772015010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/7b6f15aa0e2aedd8e53c5a98ceb95560.avif?t=1772015010\" width=616 height=69 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All mining and logistics happen in zero-g! Use your laser and vacuum to break rock and collect resources by hand or engineer systems that carry floaters back to base without you lifting a finger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/f2774bfc350faed9cf91226d52c7e24b.poster.avif?t=1772015010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/f2774bfc350faed9cf91226d52c7e24b.webm?t=1772015010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/f2774bfc350faed9cf91226d52c7e24b.mp4?t=1772015010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/6bcd8d8eacbd7923a75b84ff3b9b5187.avif?t=1772015010\" width=616 height=103 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no rush. Set your own pace as you experiment, tinker, and redesign. Advance deeper into the asteroid to discover new minerals and unlock 25+ structures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/e76533230175297dfd6c04448b56e2aa.poster.avif?t=1772015010\" width=500 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/e76533230175297dfd6c04448b56e2aa.webm?t=1772015010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144430/extras/e76533230175297dfd6c04448b56e2aa.mp4?t=1772015010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
